title: Ep 20 -Take Action!
itunes:title: Ep 20 -Take Action!
description:
The first step is the hardest. We spend too much time planning and worrying, and not enough time just taking action. In this episode we talk about how to get started and "Just Do It" like Nike says. Successful people don't spend all of their time planning, they take action and then plan.
